#: admin/com_vikbooking:VBO_WIDGETS_WELCOME_DESC1
msgid "<strong>Welcome to the Admin Widgets Customizer!</strong><br/>This interface will let you manage all the elements displayed in your Dashboard through <b>Sections</b>, <b>Containers</b> and <b>Widgets</b>."
