#: admin/com_vikbooking:VBO_CRONJOB_WEBHOOK_DESCRIPTION
msgid "This cron job allows to set up automated actions whenever new events related to bookings take place. This is useful to post the changes to remote URLs or to pass the data to third party plugins."
